---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="实用信息 - 盐色运城" description="运城旅行实用信息——开放时间、门票价格、住宿推荐、最佳旅行时间等。">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-ink mb-4">实用信息</h1>
      <p class="text-stone max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">出行前必读的运城旅行实用指南</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- 最佳旅行时间 -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-salt-dark/10">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-amber/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink">最佳旅行时间</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-pool/10 text-pool text-xs rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">推荐</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-ink">4月 — 5月 及 9月 — 10月</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone">气候宜人，适合户外游览，盐湖色彩丰富。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-salt-pink/15 text-salt-pink text-xs rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">热门</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-ink">6月 — 8月</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone">盐湖色彩最浓烈（珊瑚红/玫瑰粉），但气温较高。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-stone/10 text-stone text-xs rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">淡季</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-ink">11月 — 3月</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone">游客较少，盐结晶景观独特，需注意保暖。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 门票参考 -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-salt-dark/10">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-brick/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brick" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 5v2m0 4v2m0 4v2M5 5a2 2 0 00-2 2v3a2 2 0 110 4v3a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-3a2 2 0 110-4V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink">主要景点门票</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-salt-dark/5">
            <span class="text-ink">七彩盐湖景区</span>
            <span class="text-pool font-medium">免费</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-salt-dark/5">
            <span class="text-ink">解州关帝庙</span>
            <span class="text-amber-dark font-medium">60元</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-salt-dark/5">
            <span class="text-ink">永乐宫</span>
            <span class="text-amber-dark font-medium">50元</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-salt-dark/5">
            <span class="text-ink">鹳雀楼</span>
            <span class="text-amber-dark font-medium">60元</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-salt-dark/5">
            <span class="text-ink">普救寺</span>
            <span class="text-amber-dark font-medium">50元</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2">
            <span class="text-ink">后土祠</span>
            <span class="text-amber-dark font-medium">30元</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-stone mt-4">价格仅供参考，以景区实际公示为准。部分景区对儿童、学生、老人有优惠政策。</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 住宿推荐 -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-salt-dark/10">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-salt-pink/15 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brick" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink">住宿推荐</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium text-ink">盐湖区（市中心）</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone">交通便利，餐饮选择多，适合首次来运城的游客。有各档次酒店可选。</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium text-ink">盐湖景区周边</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone">适合想看盐湖日出日落的摄影爱好者。部分民宿可俯瞰盐湖。</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium text-ink">永济市</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone">游览鹳雀楼、普救寺等西部景点时推荐入住，可节省时间。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 注意事项 -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-salt-dark/10">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-pool/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pool" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink">旅行贴士</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-stone text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-amber mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span>运城夏季炎热干燥，紫外线强，务必携带防晒霜、遮阳帽和墨镜。</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-amber mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span>盐湖周边蚊虫较多，建议携带驱蚊用品。</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-amber mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span>参观永乐宫壁画时请勿使用闪光灯，保护珍贵文物。</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-amber mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span>运城的古建多为砖木结构，内部光线较暗，建议穿着舒适的鞋子。</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-amber mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span>部分景区距离市区较远，建议提前规划路线或包车出行。</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-amber mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span>运城美食以面食和羊肉为主，口味偏咸，可根据个人喜好提前告知店家。</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- 紧急联系 -->
    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-ink mb-6">实用电话</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-white border border-salt-dark/10 text-center">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-brick mb-1">110</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-stone">报警</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-white border border-salt-dark/10 text-center">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-brick mb-1">120</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-stone">急救</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-white border border-salt-dark/10 text-center">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-brick mb-1">119</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-stone">火警</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-white border border-salt-dark/10 text-center">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-pool mb-1">12301</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-stone">旅游投诉</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
